sql:
SELECT COUNT(post_id) AS post_count 
FROM posts 
WHERE user_id = 123;

SELECT title, likes
FROM posts
ORDER BY likes DESC;

external_knowledge:
Active individuals: Those who engage frequently on the platform through creating posts, making comments, and following others; 
Total activity score: Sum of the count of posts, comments, and followers of an individual; 
Top ten: The highest-ranking ten individuals based on the activity score.
